02:37.130 --> 02:38.830
和一把刀
and a knife?

02:43.800 --> 02:45.630
这是我
This is me.

02:48.060 --> 02:48.900
这是锡拉
This is Scylla.

02:51.630 --> 02:52.960
这是你
This is you.

02:55.460 --> 02:57.330
