...or through you.

03:07.300 --> 03:08.500
所以  为什么你不能
So why don't you give me

03:08.560 --> 03:11.530
在我割下你的睾丸前
that informed decision right now,

03:11.600 --> 03:14.730
告诉我你考虑后的答案呢
before I spill your hillbilly guts all over the carpet?

03:16.230 --> 03:19.660
你别想和我耍花样
'Cause you're messing with the wrong bitch.

03:22.800 --> 03:25.930
我能为你做些什么呢
How may I be of service?

03:28.260 --> 03:29.960
