别对我撒谎  小白脸
Now don't lie to me,Pretty.

11:08.010 --> 11:10.140
不管书里有什么  都不是你和我能解决的问题
Whatever's in that book-- it is bigger than you and me.

11:10.210 --> 11:12.540
就和锡拉一样
What,like Scylla big?

11:12.610 --> 11:15.280
这不是游戏
This is not a game,Theodore.

11:15.340 --> 11:18.340
你得告诉我  你一直和谁联络
Now,you need to tell me who you've been talking to.

11:26.010 --> 11:29.670
我不需要听你的鬼话
I don't need to do a damn thing.

11:31.440 --> 11:34.310
这就是所谓枪杆子里出政权了
That's the benefit of being the man with the gun.

11:38.540 --> 11:40.140
你现在给我写下
You're going to write down everything

11:40.210 --> 11:42.740
你知道所有关于锡拉的事情
you already know about Scylla,

11:42.810 --> 11:46.920
还有所有你从书里看到东西
and everything you learn from that book...

11:49.310 --> 11:53.380
否则  我就让墙上
...or I'm going to paint these walls

11:53.440 --> 11:55.040
沾满你的脑浆
with your gray matter.

12:00.240 --> 12:01.680
开工了!
Get to work!

12:36.980 --> 12:39.780
[档案名: 康姆利集团]
The Comrie Group

12:48.010 --> 12:49.440
好的  我马上就到
All right. I'll be right there.

12:59.710 --> 13:00.810
赛尔夫
Self.

13:00.880 --> 13:02.240
自从联系后
Hey. Michael's position

13:02.310 --> 13:03.910
迈克的位置一直没变
hasn't changed since you called.

13:03.980 --> 13:04.740
我们怎么知道他没有....
How do we know he...?

13:04.810 --> 13:05.840
蒂博格是个神经病
Bagwell's a psychopath,

13:05.910 --> 13:07.040
但是他是有计划的
but he's a psychopath with a plan.

13:07.110 --> 13:08.580
很明显  他需要从迈克那里得到什么
He obviously needs something from Michael,

13:08.640 --> 13:09.810
只要迈克不给他
and as long as Michael doesn't give it to him,

13:09.880 --> 13:11.280
他就能活着
he'll keep breathing.

13:11.340 --> 13:13.440
好吧  我和你一起去
All right. I'm coming with you.

13:13.510 --> 13:15.410
不  不  我能搞定
No,no,no,no. I got it.

13:15.480 --> 13:17.140
计划不变
Stick to the plan.

13:33.640 --> 13:35.610
你会忘记玛丽克鲁兹吗
Will you forget about Maricruz?

13:35.680 --> 13:37.180
你认为她不知道
You think she didn't know

13:37.240 --> 13:38.510
她姐姐要把你供出去吗
her sister was trying to set you up,man?

13:38.580 --> 13:40.010
你最好在维加斯有所斩获  兄弟
You better get some ass in Vegas,bro.

13:40.080 --> 13:41.740
我们是来复制卡的
We're here to copy the card.

13:41.810 --> 13:43.580
然后就离开  明白吗
Then we leave. Got it?

13:47.910 --> 13:50.010
你得到迈克的消息了吗
Have you heard from Michael?

13:50.080 --> 13:52.210
没有  怎么了?
No. Why?

13:52.280 --> 13:54.510
没事  我要快点搞定这个任务
Nothing. I want this thing done.

13:54.580 --> 13:56.680
维加斯决不是久留之地
Vegas ain't my town.

13:56.740 --> 13:57.840
真是个傻子  是吧
What a fool,huh?

13:57.910 --> 14:00.640
怎么会有人不爱这个地方呢
How could anyone not love this place,right?

14:02.680 --> 14:04.680
看看这些画面  就在那
Check this out. Right there.

14:04.740 --> 14:06.280
那个亚洲人
The Asian guy.

14:06.340 --> 14:08.980
我好像在哪见过他
I know I've seen him someplace before.

14:33.410 --> 14:35.140
弄得怎么样了?
So what do you have for me?

14:35.210 --> 14:36.410
伽特是什么
So what's "GATE"?

14:36.480 --> 14:37.810
你说什么?
Excuse me?

14:37.880 --> 14:39.240
在那个盒子上写着呢
It's on that box.

14:41.040 --> 14:43.180
-你为什么想知道呢  -只是好奇
Why do you want to know? Just curious.

14:44.480 --> 14:46.010
假如我要告诉你
What if I was to tell you

14:46.080 --> 14:48.010
我认为你只是在拖延时间呢
I think you're just stalling?

14:48.080 --> 14:51.140
拖延时间  直到你可以想出一条妙计
Biding time till you can figure out some MacGyver way

14:51.210 --> 14:53.340
-离开这儿  是吧  -我告诉你  你在用枪
to get your ass out of here,huh? I'd say you've got that gun

14:53.410 --> 14:54.980
指着能够帮助你的人
pointed at the one person who can help you.

14:55.040 --> 14:57.210
所以何不停止浪费我的时间呢
So why don't you stop wasting my time?

15:06.580 --> 15:08.440
求求你  别让他伤害我
Please,don't let him!

15:09.510 --> 15:10.840
她怎么样啊?

15:10.910 --> 15:12.580
她怎么样  迈克?
How 'bout her,Michael?

15:12.640 --> 15:14.380
能给个我不必杀她的理由吗
Any reason why I shouldn't kill her?

15:16.610 --> 15:18.440
让我们测验一下吧
Let's do a test.

15:18.510 --> 15:20.540
不!
No!

15:23.640 --> 15:26.040
进展到什么程度了　迈克·斯科菲尔德?
How far gone is Michael Scofield?

15:26.110 --> 15:27.910
迈克  他想知道什么就告诉他吧
Michael,just tell him what he wants!

15:30.780 --> 15:33.610
进展到什么程度了  迈克·斯科菲尔德
How far gone is Michael Scofield?!

15:33.680 --> 15:35.910
求你了  别让他杀我  求你了
Please,don't let him. Please!

15:37.510 --> 15:39.040
迈克  你啥时候变了个人似的了?
When did it happen,Michael?

15:39.110 --> 15:40.610
求你了  别让他杀了我
Please,don't let him...

15:40.680 --> 15:43.410
你啥时候开始不关心伤害别人的事了啊?
When did you stop caring about hurting people,huh?

15:43.480 --> 15:45.040
福克斯河监狱?  还是索纳监狱?
Fox River? Sona?

15:45.110 --> 15:47.210
你要在子弹穿透她的脑袋时
You gonna keep dragging

15:47.280 --> 15:49.140
选择视而不见吗
your feet while I put a bullet in her brain?

15:49.210 --> 15:50.980
你为何不把枪放下
Why don't you put that gun down.

15:51.040 --> 15:53.640
帅哥  你开始动笔的时候我就会把枪放下了!
I'll put it down when you start writing down,Pretty!

15:55.780 --> 15:57.240
最后的机会  三
Last chance. Three!

15:57.310 --> 15:58.380
二  一
Two! One...

15:58.440 --> 15:59.740
我说  我说
All right! All right!

16:05.810 --> 16:09.080
这些纸  是要拼在一起的
The pages,they fit together.

16:09.140 --> 16:11.780
但是它不是个地图
But it's not a map.

16:12.810 --> 16:14.310
是一张设计图
It's a blueprint.

16:15.380 --> 16:16.680
什么设计图
For what?

16:38.510 --> 16:39.640
我们的朋友贝里克  戴着
Our friend,Bellick,is wearing

16:39.710 --> 16:41.440
一个政府发的脚踝监视器
a government-issued ankle monitor.

16:41.510 --> 16:44.010
我猜斯科菲尔德也有一个
My guess is that Scofield has one,too.

16:44.080 --> 16:47.710
我就知道那个贱人在拖延时间
I knew that son of a bitch was slow-walking me.

16:47.780 --> 16:49.710
任何时候  联邦官员都有可能
Any minute,federal agents could come

16:49.780 --> 16:52.210
破门而入
blasting through that door.

16:52.280 --> 16:53.710
那我们该怎么办?
So what do we do?

16:53.780 --> 16:57.140
我要你弄到那个监视器的生产资料和序列号
I need you to get the make and serial number of that monitor.

16:57.210 --> 16:58.780
放松一点  振作精神  戴茜小姐
Feel free to pitch in here,Miss Daisy.

16:58.840 --> 17:01.310
如果让斯科菲尔德知道我卷入其中就完了
If Scofield knows I'm involved,this is over.

17:01.380 --> 17:02.740
我们需要他的帮助
We need to keep him on point.

17:02.810 --> 17:04.480
现在  你出去把线索找出来
Now,get out there and get that information.

17:07.580 --> 17:09.710
那些特工怎么办
What about the agents?

17:09.780 --> 17:12.640
兵来将挡
Let 'em come.

17:39.740 --> 17:41.640
我们怎么知道他会出来赌博
How do we even know this guy's out gambling?

17:41.710 --> 17:44.280
那家伙有30万美元的信用额度  还有免费的客房
The guy's got $300,000 in credit and a comped room.

17:44.340 --> 17:45.540
他就在这里  继续找下去
He's here. Keep looking.

17:45.610 --> 17:47.040
莎拉
Hey,Sara.

17:47.110 --> 17:49.540
我知道现在不是谈这个话题的最佳时机
Hey,uh,I realize this might not be the best time for this,

17:49.610 --> 17:51.040
但迈克还没给我打过电话
but I still haven't heard from Michael.

17:51.110 --> 17:52.380
他们正在解决蒂博格吧
They must be dealing with T-Bag.

17:52.440 --> 17:54.580
-林肯  别这样  -什么
Lincoln,come on. What?

17:54.640 --> 17:56.240
维加斯不是你的地盘
Vegas just isn't your town?

17:56.310 --> 17:57.440
任何你告诉我的事
From everything I've heard about you,

17:57.510 --> 17:59.380
都可能极大地改变进程
that would be a pretty big change of pace.

17:59.440 --> 18:00.940
我也这么想
I guess so.

18:01.010 --> 18:03.540
林肯  告诉我好吗
Lincoln,please talk to me.

18:05.040 --> 18:06.510
迈克有和你说过妈妈的事情吗
Has Michael told you about Mom?

18:06.580 --> 18:07.910
没有
No.

18:07.980 --> 18:09.380
他们很像
They were much alike.

18:09.440 --> 18:11.980
有着同样的想法
They got the same mind.

18:12.040 --> 18:14.180
当妈妈变老的时候  她开始失去意识
As Mom got older,she started to lose it.

18:14.240 --> 18:16.040
我们后来才知道
We,uh,later found out

18:16.110 --> 18:18.580
这是脑瘤的征兆
it was a symptom of a brain tumor,hama...

18:18.640 --> 18:20.040
错构瘤
Hamartoma. Yeah.

18:20.110 --> 18:22.780
她小时候  经常流鼻血
As a kid,she got nosebleeds.

18:22.840 --> 18:23.910
后来不留鼻血了
They stopped.

18:23.980 --> 18:26.780
当她30岁的时候  又开始流了
In her 30s,they started up again.

18:26.840 --> 18:29.310
她后来死于动脉瘤
She later died of a brain aneurysm.

18:29.380 --> 18:31.410
你告诉我这些  是想让我知道
And you're telling me this,because Michael and his mother

18:31.480 --> 18:33.410
迈克和他妈妈有一样的症状  对吗
are similar in that way,too,right?

18:33.480 --> 18:36.810
他小时候也流鼻血的
He got nosebleeds as a kid.

18:36.880 --> 18:39.010
后来也不流了  但几天前
They stopped,and the last couple of days

18:39.080 --> 18:40.740
他又开始了
they started up again.

18:42.180 --> 18:44.140
你妈妈几岁时候过世的
How old was your mom when she passed away?

18:44.210 --> 18:45.580
31岁
Thirty-one.

18:46.980 --> 18:50.140
迈克刚刚31岁啊
Michael's just turned 31.

18:55.210 --> 18:56.640
我找到他了
I found him.

18:56.710 --> 18:58.240
盯着他
Keep an eye on him.

18:58.310 --> 19:01.010
好的
Okay.

20:15.510 --> 20:17.810
你是安德鲁·布劳纳吗
Andrew Blauner?

20:17.880 --> 20:20.110
恩  是的
Uh,yeah.

20:20.180 --> 20:22.480
有什么可以为您效劳的吗
Can I help you?

20:22.540 --> 20:24.980
希望可以
I hope so.

20:30.200 --> 20:34.170
我想知道你有没有男朋友或者室友之类的
Any boyfriends or roommates I should know about?

20:34.230 --> 20:36.000
没有
No.

20:38.230 --> 20:40.600
今天有预定外卖吗
Any deliveries scheduled for today?

20:40.670 --> 20:42.630
没有
No.

20:48.130 --> 20:50.070
我再给你一次
I'm giving you one more...

20:51.700 --> 20:54.900
这些都是什么啊
What is all this?

20:57.330 --> 20:59.330
你还好吗
You okay?

21:01.170 --> 21:03.370
他们让我别和你说话
They told me not to talk to you.

21:05.170 --> 21:08.000
他们?  他们是谁?
"They"? Who's they?

21:08.070 --> 21:10.030
这是惠斯勒的设计图
This is Whistler's blueprint.

21:10.100 --> 21:12.270
我们可以在这个建筑里找到锡拉
It's the building where we can find Scylla.

21:12.330 --> 21:15.670
换句话说就是在伽特公司里
In other words,it's GATE.

21:15.730 --> 21:18.300
锡拉在哪
Where's Scylla?

21:18.370 --> 21:21.100
我在看到楼之前不能确定
I can't be certain until I see the building itself,

21:21.170 --> 21:24.000
但是我确定就在办公室下面的某个地方
but I'm pretty sure it's somewhere down here,below this office.

21:24.070 --> 21:26.100
什么是锡拉
What is Scylla?

21:26.170 --> 21:27.870
是公司的小黑名单
It's The Company's little black book.

21:29.230 --> 21:31.000
我想你现在就带我去伽特公司
I want you to take me to GATE,now.

21:35.270 --> 21:38.800
因为你能从锡拉里嗅出钱的味道　是吧
Because you can smell that Scylla money,can't you?

21:38.870 --> 21:43.200
那就是你为什么参加的原因　就像我一样
That's what you're in it for,just like me.

21:45.030 --> 21:47.570
说出来
Say it.

21:47.630 --> 21:48.900
说吧
Come on.

21:48.970 --> 21:50.530
我想你说出来
I want you to say it.

21:54.870 --> 21:57.830
我加入是为了钱
I'm in it for the money.

22:00.330 --> 22:02.170
你看到了
You see?

22:03.800 --> 22:06.530
我们其实没什么区别
We ain't so different after all.

22:59.400 --> 23:00.600
说
Yes?

23:00.670 --> 23:02.670
当·赛尔夫不在家
Don Self is not at his house.

23:02.730 --> 23:04.700
看起来他跑路了
Looks like he cleared out.

23:04.770 --> 23:08.530
通知局里我们的手下还有洛城警方
Notify our people inside the Bureau and LAPD.

23:10.070 --> 23:12.670
我觉得他跑不了多远
I doubt that he could have gotten very far.

23:12.730 --> 23:14.330
长官
Sir?

23:14.400 --> 23:15.630
现在不行
Not now.

23:15.700 --> 23:18.870
当·赛尔夫要见你
Don Self is here to see you.

23:37.700 --> 23:40.570
提个醒  朋友　她性冷淡
Got to warn you,friend,she's cold.

23:44.730 --> 23:47.370
[数据卡存储空间已满  请清理或更换磁卡]

23:50.610 --> 23:52.670
[短信: 设备故障  撤]

23:55.670 --> 23:57.830
祝你好运　伙计
Good luck,pal.

24:03.870 --> 24:06.030
盯着他
Stay with him.

24:21.400 --> 24:23.330
斯科菲尔德就在那里
Scofield's really getting somewhere in there.

24:23.400 --> 24:24.730
效率挺高的嘛
Man works fast.

24:24.800 --> 24:26.300
他说如果看不到我以前在哪工作的
Says he can't get any further

24:26.370 --> 24:28.400
就无法进展下去
without seeing my former place of employment.

24:28.470 --> 24:31.300
你把我们的绊脚石处理掉了吗
Did you take care of our little troll problem?

24:36.270 --> 24:38.200
想都别想对我干这种事
Don't even think about doing this to me.

24:38.270 --> 24:39.430
你可不能过河拆桥甩了我啊
My name's on the door.

24:39.500 --> 24:41.170
要不是我觉得你还有利用价值
If I didn't think you were valuable,

24:41.230 --> 24:43.230
你早就死翘翘了
you'd be dead already.

24:50.130 --> 24:52.770
这只是有点信息超载  伙计们
It's-It's just a little sensory overload,guys.

24:52.830 --> 24:54.430
只是卡上没有空间了
There just wasn't any room for the card.

24:54.500 --> 24:55.870
不错 因为如果我们把装置打开
Right. Because if we turn the device on

24:55.930 --> 24:58.870
它就把赌场里所有的卡上信息都收集来了
in the casino,it fills up on all the data from the slots.

25:00.900 --> 25:02.930
就像他们付账的时候
Like when they're about to pay out.

25:03.000 --> 25:05.200
-这绝对不是预料之中的　-是吗
Oh,it's completely unintentional. Really?

25:05.270 --> 25:07.730
是的　这不就是你造这玩意儿的初衷吗
Yeah. It's not why you built the damn thing in the first place?

25:07.800 --> 25:09.930
如果我们不需要你
If we didn't need you...

25:10.000 --> 25:13.430
可你们需要我　我们从长计议  好吗
But you do,so just take a brewski and chill,all right?

25:13.500 --> 25:15.930
我们要想个办法让斯库得利一个人待着
Okay,we need to figure out a way to get Scuderi alone.

25:18.000 --> 25:20.100
喂
Yeah.

25:20.170 --> 25:22.600
老男人在水池边出现了
The old man just showed up at the pool.

25:22.670 --> 25:24.400
从他穿着来看
From what he's wearing,there's no way

25:24.470 --> 25:26.000
他身上不可能有卡
he's got the card on him.

25:26.070 --> 25:27.230
跟着他
Stay with him.

25:28.670 --> 25:30.900
卡在他房里
Card's in his room.

25:37.930 --> 25:39.070
告诉我  唐纳德
Tell me,Donald,

25:39.130 --> 25:41.570
你臆想中我们碰头的这一刻会是怎样一番景象呢
how did you play this moment out in your head?

25:41.630 --> 25:44.270
你想到你自己会过来吗
Did you picture yourself coming in here,

25:44.330 --> 25:46.530
昂首挺胸  盛气凌人地
chest out,jaw squared,

25:46.600 --> 25:48.170
准备让我给你答案
ready to demand answers?

25:48.230 --> 25:51.600
你可曾在幻想中想过
Did you at any time in your fantasy

25:51.670 --> 25:54.130
你会这么紧张呢
imagine that you would be this nervous?

25:55.970 --> 25:58.100
老实说 我从前没想过
Honestly,I,uh... I didn't think much past

25:58.170 --> 25:59.600
把这些东西给你
giving you these.

26:05.170 --> 26:08.600
柏林　尼日利亚
Berlin. Nigeria.

26:08.670 --> 26:10.630
康姆利集团
The Comrie Group.

26:12.070 --> 26:13.730
怎么不把肯尼迪遇刺
Why not JFK

26:13.800 --> 26:15.830
和林德伯格绑架案也一块儿搞来?
and the Lindbergh baby while you're at it?

26:15.900 --> 26:17.000
孩子
Son,

26:17.070 --> 26:18.900
这些事情都已经调查完毕了
those matters have been fully vetted.

26:18.970 --> 26:20.300
都是些陈年往事了
They're relics.

26:20.370 --> 26:22.800
我跟这些一点关系都没有
I had nothing to do with them,and if

26:22.870 --> 26:24.830
如果这些是你调查我的原因
this is why you've been pulling data on me,

26:24.900 --> 26:26.600
我可以省你不少麻烦呢
I could have saved you a lot of trouble.

26:26.670 --> 26:28.200
好吧　这些记录
Okay. Well,these records

26:28.270 --> 26:30.200
和足以解释我调查你涉嫌参与这些事件原因
and a sealed letter explaining my investigation

26:30.270 --> 26:32.170
的这封密封的信
into your involvement with these matters

